From Geno Subject Re The doctrine of Original Sin In article M Geno writes Nothing unclean shall enter heaven Therefore babies are born in such a state that should they die they are cuf off from God and put in hell which is exactly the doctrine of Augustine and jeff adams Regarding the first paragraph I would say that I didn't write I don't believe that unbaptized babies are put in I don't even believe in At least I don't believe in a fiery place where there will be gnashing of teeth geno